  "detailed_description": "'Energy Cycle' – new puzzle game from the developers of ‘Energy Balance’. When you click each cell on the game field - it changes color, and the colors of adjacent cells horizontally and vertically. Your task to bring all the cells to the same color. Sounds pretty easy, but try to do it!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n'Energy Cycle' feature three modes for every taste:<br />\r\n- Puzzle<br />\r\n(Without timer. Pre-designed puzzles.)<br />\r\n- Time Attack<br />\r\n(With timer and scoring. Random puzzles.)<br />\r\n- Infinite Play<br />\r\n(Without timer. Like ‘Time Attack’, but you can play it forever.)",
  "about_the_game": "'Energy Cycle' – new puzzle game from the developers of ‘Energy Balance’. When you click each cell on the game field - it changes color, and the colors of adjacent cells horizontally and vertically. Your task to bring all the cells to the same color. Sounds pretty easy, but try to do it!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n'Energy Cycle' feature three modes for every taste:<br />\r\n- Puzzle<br />\r\n(Without timer. Pre-designed puzzles.)<br />\r\n- Time Attack<br />\r\n(With timer and scoring. Random puzzles.)<br />\r\n- Infinite Play<br />\r\n(Without timer. Like ‘Time Attack’, but you can play it forever.)",
